<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MAW PATHIAN, NANG VELNGEI BIK CH467</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw Pathian, nang velngei bik, Dawtnak a tling bikmi, Na
 thlua-chuahnak a sung bik, An cungah tlunter law, Na lianh-ngannak ruat
 tiin, Na thluachuah hmuhter hna, Thih tiang in um ti awkah, An bia-kamnak
 fehter.

[V2]
 Vawlei na um lioah khan, Kana khua na phan i, Thit-umnak na lawmhpi
 hna, Misur hang na karhter, A tu an i thitnak hi, Lawmhpi law thluachuah
 pe, An i duhnak karhter law, Na min upat hna seh.

[V3]
 Nang an in bochan nakhnga, Maw Pathian bawm hna law, Ngaihchiat harnak
 an in ah, Nang nih umpi ve hna, An nunnak ni nih liam in, Lei kaltak hna
 hmanhseh, Zungzal um ti awk caah, Na inn ah hruai ve hna.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<hymn_number>467</hymn_number>
</song>